</script> <div class="article-2020-inner article-2020-header"> <p class="mainSection"> <a href="/coronavirus">Coronavírus</a> </p> <h1 class="title "> Covid-19. Os portugueses têm agora uma missão: “achatar a curva” </h1> </div> <div class="article-2020-inner article-2020-body"> <div class="aside placement-left mq--onlyOnDesktop"> <p class="timeStamp publishedDate" datetime="2020-03-17T13:48:12.180Z"> <span class="timeStamp__date">17 março 2020</span> <span class="timeStamp__hour">13:48</span></p> <section class="signature"> <div class="authorContainer"> <figure class="figurePerson"> <a href="/autores/2015-05-02-Raquel-Albuquerque-1" target="_self" > <picture class="portrait"> <img src="//images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-72" alt="Raquel Albuquerque" class="js-lazy-picture" data-srcset="//images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-30 30w, //images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-50 50w, //images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-70 70w, //images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-100 100w, //images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-140 140w, //images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-200 200w, //images.impresa.pt/expresso/2020-11-27-Raquel-Albuquerque_RGB.png-3/1x1/mw-380 380w" data-sizes="(min-width: 768px) 72px, 30px" /> </picture></a> </figure> <div class="personDetails"> <p class="author "> <a href="/autores/2015-05-02-Raquel-Albuquerque-1"> Raquel Albuquerque </a></p> <p class="profession">Jornalista</p> </div> </div> <div class="authorContainer"> <figure class="figurePerson"> <a href="/autores/2015-11-01-Tiago-Pereira-Santos" target="_self" > <picture class="portrait"> <img src="//images.impresa.pt/expresso/2016-04-08-Tiago-Pereira-Santos.jpg-3/1x1/mw-72" alt="Tiago Pereira Santos" class="js-lazy-picture" data-srcset="//images.